<div class="agent-show">
  <div class="photo-main" style="background-image:url('<%= url_for( @property.photos[0]) %>')">
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h3 class="m-0"><strong><%= @account.full_name %></strong></h3>
        <div class="row d-flex justify-content-between">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h5 class="property-info"><%= @account.company %></h5>
            <p>Registered from <%= @account.created_at %></p>
          </div>
        </div>

      <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <hr>
          <h4><%= @account.first_name %>'s bio</h4>
          <div id="property-details">
            <p class="text-justify">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nunc eleifend egestas augue nec hendrerit. Proin a nunc quis nulla pellentesque ornare non nec ligula. Suspendisse nec placerat erat. Class aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora torquent per conubia nostra, per inceptos himenaeos. In sagittis molestie efficitur. Pellentesque in sollicitudin dui. In vitae commodo sem, sit amet fermentum nibh. Curabitur ante erat, vulputate id dapibus ac, rutrum a augue. Suspendisse vitae ex ornare, eleifend neque eu, dictum metus. Mauris a iaculis neque. Ut ipsum metus, venenatis a feugiat a, feugiat non ex. Aenean id nisi dui. Sed metus nunc, tempus quis sodales quis, lacinia quis nibh. Fusce sagittis mi erat, nec pretium eros elementum vitae. Donec eget ex aliquet, mattis velit consectetur, molestie odio. Fusce sollicitudin tincidunt purus, quis scelerisque orci.</p>
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-outline-dark my-2" id="toggleDetails">Show More</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4">
      <%= render "properties/agent_info" %>

      <div class="row bg-light border mt-4 text-center">
        <div class="col-6">
          <p><strong><%= @properties_for_sale.count %></strong><br>For Sale</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <p><strong><%= @properties_sold.count %></strong><br>Sold</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <p><strong><%= @properties_for_rent.count %></strong><br>For Rent</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <p><strong><%= @properties_leased.count %></strong><br>Leased</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="my-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 pb-3">
        <h4 class="border-bottom pb-1 pt-4">Best properties from <%= @account.first_name %></h4>
      </div>
      <%= render "properties/agent_properties", properties: @my_properties %>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
